    - install needed dev tools and libraries (see configure.ac)
    
    - download and install libfmcore (https://github.com/afilmore/libfmcore)
    
    - ./autogen.sh && ./configure --prefix=/usr && make
    
    - sudo make install
    
    - Enjoy :-P
    
    
